---
layout: base.njk
title: Corey Preston
description: AI Technical Leader, patent holder, and product builder. I lead AI at Cisco, built Cocovox, and help companies ship AI products.
---

<section class="hero">
  <img
    src="/assets/images/headshot.jpg"
    alt="Corey Preston"
    class="hero__headshot"
    width="128"
    height="128"
    style="view-transition-name: hero-image;"
    onerror="this.style.display='none'"
  >

  <h1 class="hero__title" style="view-transition-name: page-title;">Corey Preston</h1>
  <p class="hero__tagline">AI Technical Leader · Patent Holder · Product Builder · Author</p>
  <p class="hero__intro">
    I lead AI at Cisco, hold a US patent on generative AI content systems, and I'm building
    <a href="/cocovox/">Cocovox</a> — an AI learning platform tackling the literacy crisis.
  </p>

  <div class="hero__actions">
    <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn--primary btn--large">Let's Work Together</a>
    <a href="/portfolio/" class="btn btn--secondary btn--large">View Portfolio</a>
    <a href="{{ site.resume }}" class="btn btn--secondary btn--large" download>Download Resume</a>
  </div>

  <p class="hero__meta">
    <small>San Anselmo, CA · <a href="{{ site.social.linkedin }}">LinkedIn</a></small>
  </p>
</section>

